{"tid":315030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］夜媽媽真係唔好亂推人返屋企","createTime":"2017-07-09T17:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T15:29:29.000Z","uid":7923,"like":983,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd68da6ed33fe414d799729c57d43d7164f25c70","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"啱先喺旺角搭車去馬鞍山，<br />\n咁係海栢花園落咗車喇，<br />\n本身要轉的士返屋企嘅，<br />\n見到有個坐住輪椅大約50路既auntie，<br />\n佢用英文同我地講可唔可以推佢去後邊小巴站嗰度，<br />\n咁我哋本身以為就咁推佢去lift口就搞掂，<br />\n一路推一路撩我哋吹水，佢冇講自己要去幾遠<br />\n 咁我哋又心諗無理由放低一個傷殘人士不理，<br />\n就一直推佢，仆你個街佢一路講前面個building，<br />\n推下推下推撚到去雅典居，屌你老母成半鐘，<br />\n中途段路又黑又盛，一度以為自己會俾人埋伏，<br />\n跟住之後我哋走去問過實Q，佢話有人見過佢行到路，<br />\n仲要成日呃啲路人過嚟推佢，一日三四次，<br />\n真係好撚後悔做好人，成日都利用人哋啲好心。<br />\n<br />\n好心你啦住雅典居就搭的士啦仆街，<br />\n唔好撚夜媽媽呃鳩人哋啲好心啦。<br />\n<br />\nsorry 1999"},{"pid":"6548503c7f0caefacfaa5bb29fa3eaed7ceca5b6","tid":315030,"uid":23951,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"咁無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddf79978ab8618e4713f90c9dac8a906c6aa7ef","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:11:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望所有住馬鞍山嘅人睇到"},{"pid":"b9d1e881a1be893557be9e2bbc90770dba204547","tid":315030,"uid":6848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"50路廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1c7a3895bbef49356b29110d60e0b5e94891f4","tid":315030,"uid":101115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫推"},{"pid":"7c14804de8d5873258d0bb6af154c63dc4d575de","tid":315030,"uid":14704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"佢都幾無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b1b920efbb62383e6dc3428c20d30bcae349a9","tid":315030,"uid":31758,"like":283,"dislike":0,"score":283,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"以為你撞鬼"},{"pid":"ed19798d9e4e4307c63db0c9fe8a41082b4b63ac","tid":315030,"uid":34403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd15598c45f6c3125ca4a5172c59b6ebc0472ff","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":143,"dislike":0,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:16:59.000Z","msg":"推 希望所有馬鞍山撚知道<br />\n好心留返俾啲有需要嘅人<br />\n唔好俾廢老<br />\n明明搭的士解決到嘅問題<br />\n仲曬鳩人地時間<br />\n推撚完佢 我仲要行返去海柏搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日返早 屌你老母！"},{"pid":"c5edd5ff6f7f52fef15a06a3976a5146ec1a7a5c","tid":315030,"uid":43436,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為你撞鬼</blockquote><br />\n睇標題以為推推下冇左個人之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16c50607d0cb806a6b8a82c4e395ca6627fa3cf","tid":315030,"uid":33359,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:18:43.000Z","msg":"我都試過,個陣返緊暑期工,有個輪椅阿叔叫我幫手推佢返屋企,佢話前面好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我同老闆講聲話好快,屌一推推撚左佢兩公里,佢仲得閒停下話買野食仲唔請我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾推左個幾鐘,仲要比老細屌我係咪乘機蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9cbe77cd56a295b1a1b81d593ce154b4706942","tid":315030,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:22:56.000Z","msg":"影佢相嘛"},{"pid":"e3f83cbe09355a65f2762252c0787c7b902d2e3f","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:26:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影佢相嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n走果下都諗緊影<br />\n但又驚 都唔知仲有無其他伏<br />\n相就靠下一個被呀婆呃嘅人<br />\n應該好快有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食q話佢一日呃人3-4次"},{"pid":"7d03996cf630103d8ec5b139c738e970004cce23","tid":315030,"uid":53037,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以為你撞鬼</blockquote><br />\n睇標題以為推推下冇左個人之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以為推咗落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38096a3794834b0dd94a3d48dd34eb9d0045580a","tid":315030,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:30:14.000Z","msg":"咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住隔離"},{"pid":"489a5a2ba2ade3358e3968509d914adc038c2f62","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過,個陣返緊暑期工,有個輪椅阿叔叫我幫手推佢返屋企,佢話前面好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我同老闆講聲話好快,屌一推推撚左佢兩公里,佢仲得閒停下話買野食仲唔請我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最尾推左個幾鐘,仲要比老細屌我係咪乘機蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利用人地同情心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec41e171a676f3c4072a6bba123234d780c075d","tid":315030,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:31:18.000Z","msg":"正仆街"},{"pid":"05699f1b57d8a9a89abd8f3844f50fbdb7adeb97","tid":315030,"uid":23451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:32:07.000Z","msg":"btw姐係海柏推到雅典居後門？<br />\n點解推到半個鐘咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔係好遠咋喎"},{"pid":"f03d0abbc5bf03231804fcc1bc1e0ec3f8a98b41","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017