<br />\n最憎啲人利用同情心 正一仆街"},{"pid":"6a5eeed779e6a2d8b3f8d0ba4bf54712371cdc72","tid":315030,"uid":45613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"相都冇"},{"pid":"30341ffe0bac26fdb213438f9af4780a0d24d5af","tid":315030,"uid":65813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw姐係海柏推到雅典居後門？<br />\n點解推到半個鐘咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔係好遠咋喎</blockquote><br />\n係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />來回既話就要既"},{"pid":"2f3c9090f54e2fb009ba1b5e01c581b67cf0a48a","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw姐係海柏推到雅典居後門？<br />\n點解推到半個鐘咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔係好遠咋喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鬼唔知行過去唔洗咁耐<br />\n以前住過都唔會喺海柏搭的士返去<br />\n話遠唔遠<br />\n但係推輪椅啊 廢老又重 架車又多嘢<br />\n留意返係上暗斜<br />\n仲要最遠第八座<br />\n推完仲要行返海柏搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開波知道係咁遠一定叫佢自己搭車"},{"pid":"9cb585315b2f2c7ecbd65e1e62fa8bded4e1ce0c","tid":315030,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"仆佢臭街死撚廢老"},{"pid":"a12b923590c58990136d182f6ff2939a620d2441","tid":315030,"uid":85909,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:38:50.000Z","msg":"下次見到佢照推，但就一路推一路跑，仲要飄移咁過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知佢會唔會即刻嚇到跳車企喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1dd411df27e75dfb403a85daf44795f87fc8d04","tid":315030,"uid":89197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"推佢出馬路等佢自己行啦"},{"pid":"e32e97b8458fbb2095e3824b9ac044de40f6dd5c","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能有病想有人同佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n向好果方面諗會冇咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都好你都係幫左人<br />\n<br />\n下次小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實果段路都好安全既，係少人d<br />\n但冇咩位有人埋伏到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前面車閘嗰邊條路好暗<br />\n夜晚會有小巴停喺度<br />\n要伏唔會伏唔到<br />\n諗自己安全都好正常<br />\n嬲都無用 後悔無用<br />\n只係希望唔好再有人俾個呀婆呃同情同時間"},{"pid":"e6f4a4f6304519ed77e9906ddeefcb75df252a76","tid":315030,"uid":89064,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次見到佢照推，但就一路推一路跑，仲要飄移咁過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知佢會唔會即刻嚇到跳車企喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正呀喂，見到一定要咁做，教訓下d死廢老"},{"pid":"5cece71e747935e29ca5b346a376a9ea98b7ccb2","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次見到佢照推，但就一路推一路跑，仲要飄移咁過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知佢會唔會即刻嚇到跳車企喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢應該唔怕<br />\n頭先紅燈呀婆叫我照過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔要命我要呀"},{"pid":"3500c1d38f220975f6eb729a4198cc07562e27f3","tid":315030,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推佢出馬路等佢自己行啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係我辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b50bff0fbd12ca0c35004af593c0375b52b1a6","tid":315030,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n呃人推佢既意義係咩"},{"pid":"9ab8a324f3e21